{"tid":2192731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子經社區檢測對病毒初步陽性　入院後檢測結果陰性","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:33:58.000Z","uid":54800,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7472ef635de29e72f74f87a92990921bf244b424","tid":2192731,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"一名經由普及社區檢測時，對病毒呈初步陽性的44歲男子，送到聯合醫院再做檢測時，鼻咽拭子和深喉樣本的檢測，以及血清抗體測試的結果都呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君說，患者的樣本送到中心再做檢測時，因樣本量不足，轉送醫院再做檢測，暫時難以介定個案是否屬假陽性個案，以往亦曾有初步陽性的個案，再做檢測後轉為陰性的情況，可能與取樣或其他原因有關。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理劉家獻說，男子送到聯合醫院期間，一直是在單獨病房隔離。"},{"pid":"f379a9685c6475d18493741ac4c34571dc503bda","tid":2192731,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1548314_1_L_20200907175103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1548314_1_L_20200907175103.jpg&h=8d2473d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fe498cde6cea1d28500ab03fd2602a94efbec19","tid":2192731,"uid":362431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96edcceda5d637e578a95feba1f80de84ffda253","tid":2192731,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"支那試劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4f45bbbc1be7a9074427db76112f6150ecc752","tid":2192731,"uid":197005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c997ae8dc49242f2c5eccd1a37e868f117e3d34f","tid":2192731,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"過2日出病癥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6b1bf1958d080385968dd081e8fdfa40e8f61f","tid":2192731,"uid":125193,"like